            <title><![CDATA[【#根除幽门螺旋杆菌后还会再感染吗#[疑问]】#为什么不建议未成年人根治幽门螺旋杆菌# 大多数幽门螺旋杆菌感染发生在儿童和青少年时期，不经治疗很难自愈。并且...]]></title>
            <description><![CDATA[【<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E6%A0%B9%E9%99%A4%E5%B9%BD%E9%97%A8%E8%9E%BA%E6%97%8B%E6%9D%86%E8%8F%8C%E5%90%8E%E8%BF%98%E4%BC%9A%E5%86%8D%E6%84%9F%E6%9F%93%E5%90%97%23&amp;extparam=%23%E6%A0%B9%E9%99%A4%E5%B9%BD%E9%97%A8%E8%9E%BA%E6%97%8B%E6%9D%86%E8%8F%8C%E5%90%8E%E8%BF%98%E4%BC%9A%E5%86%8D%E6%84%9F%E6%9F%93%E5%90%97%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#根除幽门螺旋杆菌后还会再感染吗#</span></a><span class="url-icon"><img alt="[疑问]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/default/d_yiwen-40c066d5c3.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span>】<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E4%B8%BA%E4%BB%80%E4%B9%88%E4%B8%8D%E5%BB%BA%E8%AE%AE%E6%9C%AA%E6%88%90%E5%B9%B4%E4%BA%BA%E6%A0%B9%E6%B2%BB%E5%B9%BD%E9%97%A8%E8%9E%BA%E6%97%8B%E6%9D%86%E8%8F%8C%23&amp;extparam=%23%E4%B8%BA%E4%BB%80%E4%B9%88%E4%B8%8D%E5%BB%BA%E8%AE%AE%E6%9C%AA%E6%88%90%E5%B9%B4%E4%BA%BA%E6%A0%B9%E6%B2%BB%E5%B9%BD%E9%97%A8%E8%9E%BA%E6%97%8B%E6%9D%86%E8%8F%8C%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#为什么不建议未成年人根治幽门螺旋杆菌#</span></a> 大多数幽门螺旋杆菌感染发生在儿童和青少年时期，不经治疗很难自愈。并且，家庭传播是幽门螺旋杆菌感染的主要途径之一，感染幽门螺旋杆菌的家庭成员始终是潜在的传染源。专家鼓励成年的幽门螺旋杆菌感染者进行根除治疗，根除后再感染率很低。<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E5%94%A0%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%23&amp;extparam=%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E5%94%A0%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#小卫唠健康#</span></a>  <a href="http://t.cn/A69e30Kb" data-hide=""><span class="url-icon"><img style="width: 1rem;height: 1rem" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/upload/2015/09/25/3/timeline_card_small_web_default.png" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span> <span class="surl-text">网页链接</span></a>]]></description>
